 <h1><u>RECEIPE OF NOODLES</u></h1>
<p> I like <em>Noodles</em> because it is very easy to make and ready to eat.
 .We can make it with less ingredients. 
.We can make many special varieties.</p>
<p>With Noodles we can make many varieties such as Egg noodles,Chicken noodles.
Noodles are the best street foods with less costs.
By adding sauce,beverges noodles tastes more tasty.
Noodles Tastes Spicy</p>
<section>
<h2>Required Ingredients</h2>
</section>
<div>
<ul> 
<li>noodles</li>
<li>masala</li>
<li>water</li>
<li>eggs</li>
<!--inner list-->
  <ul>
  <li>two</li> 
 <li>three</li> 
  </ul>
<!-- end of inner list-->
<li>oil</li>
<li>chilli powder</li>
<li>salt</li>
</ul>
</div>

<img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2456435/pexels-photo-2456435.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=3&h=750&w=1260"  height="350 width="500"alt="noodles"/>
<!--<img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2204771/pexels-photo-2204771.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940" alt="noodles"/>-->
<main>
<ol>
<em>
<li>Firstly heat the water and put the noodles🥓 into it😀</li>
<li>After sometime put these noodles aside</li>
<li>Then put the oil into the vessel and heat it</li>
     <!--use the eggs only up to needed quantity not more than that>
<li>Break the eggs and put them into the oil🥚</li>
<li>Roast these eggs by adding chill powder and salt into it👨‍🍳👨‍🍳</li>
    <!--use salt and chill powder as much as needed-->
<li>After that put the noodles into eggs roast</li>
<li>Mix them thoroughly by adding masala to it😗</li>
    <!--until it becomes spicy-->
<li>So that finally Egg noodles are ready🤤</li>
</em>
</ol>
</main>
